In this experiment there will be 4 blocks.
In this task, you will hear a sequence of syllables with different pitches, a pause, then a syllable pitch pair.
Your task is to determine whether the SYLLABLE/PITCH in this pair is in the previous sequence.
After hearing the syllable pitch pair, you will be prompted to indicate whether the SYLLABLE/PITCH was "absent" or "present" from the sequence.
Press "Next" to enter the block.
Remeber to attend PITCHes. Press "Next" to start trials.
Remeber to attend SYLLABLEs (WORDS). Press "Next" to start trials.
